{"tid":632892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局第十次入市買入35.33億港元　累積涉資約337億","createTime":"2018-04-17T22:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T00:04:45.000Z","uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"daffb71df687adb9fe17322dc51b5b1d40147209","tid":632892,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T22:37:15.000Z","msg":"金管局於紐約尾市兩度掃入港元　涉逾51億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180418/photo/bkn-20180418055530318-0418_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180418062003\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180418%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180418055530318-0418_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180418062003&h=215a0959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港金融管理局。<br />\n<br />\n港匯續弱！由於港元兌每美元再度觸及7.85的弱方兌換保證水平，香港金融管理局在紐約時段周二尾市(香港時間周三凌晨5時左右)，一小時內兩度掃入港元來捍衛聯匯，先後分別買入15.7億和35.33億港元，共涉51.03億港元。<br />\n<br />\n金管局日內已經4度出手買入港元，令購買港元的規模增至146.8億港元。<br />\n<br />\n自上周四起，金管局已經至少10次買入港元，累積涉資約337億港元，令4月19日的銀行體系結餘降至1,461.51億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180418/bkn-20180418055530318-0418_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180418%2Fbkn-20180418055530318-0418_00842_001.html&d=c%2FrTu7y0pydzv%2BJQ74Pgztr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=467aca38\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180418/bkn-20180418055530318-0418_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"16176f8619305801c264a67a79e491f960edf26c","tid":632892,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T23:02:29.000Z","msg":"金管局再接港元沽盤　買入約51億港元<br />\n<br />\n港匯再次觸發弱方兌換保證，金管局在紐約交易時段再在市場承接港元沽盤，共買入約51.02億港元，令周四銀行體系戶口結餘降至1461.51億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391757-20180418.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391757-20180418.htm&d=c%2FrTu7y0pydzv%2BJQ74Pgztr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0dbfa538\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391757-20180418.htm&h=b62b7d7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391757-20180418.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a4176f58c0187abe5b51034a4ead84d6e7ab6058","tid":632892,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T23:07:15.000Z","msg":"買太多會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日不停買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11713a0e162fcf863401dfeb5e56a7f8c1fb3d10","tid":632892,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4176f58c0187abe5b51034a4ead84d6e7ab6058","tid":632892,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T23:07:15.000Z","msg":"買太多會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日不停買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T23:45:16.000Z","msg":"唔會點 , 跌到咁上下就加息"},{"pid":"a3a2952f1273abeb3a64e3297dcbf482b14437d5","tid":632892,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T23:46:10.000Z","msg":"走資失控"},{"pid":"35e6307f7f4d4f1b30a09f90f1f2e4bf6a4efa83","tid":632892,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買太多會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日不停買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會點 , 跌到咁上下就加息</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學5毛狗話齋，冇事既！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />